title: Expenditures: Food Prepared on Out-of-Town Trips by Deciles of Income Before Taxes: Third 10 Percent (21st to 30th Percentile)
notes:
Income before taxes refers to the total money earnings and selected money receipts during the 12 months prior to the interview date.
